title.11: Classic Star Wars: The Early Adventures (1994) #1
title.13: Star Wars: Tales of the Jedi - The Freedon Nadd Uprising (1994) #1

description.4: In the'droid'trade the only use for old units is as spare parts and scrap. So even'See-Threepio'is impressed when he and'Artoo'meet veritable antiques Q-E'and'2-E, two diminutive'Model Es'who have operated a nursery for several generations of'Kalarbans. But despite their longevity, Q-E and 2-E carry a horrific secret that could spell the end for all'droids!
description.5: As the Infinity Watch draws closer to the inevitable showdown with Count Abyss, truths of the villains past are brought to light. Witness the untold origins of the sinister Count Abyss!
description.11: Featuring classic adventures from the early age of Star Wars! In the first issue, Threepio and Artoo must locate a missing Luke and Leia on an anti-droid planet!
description.13: A Jedi master is kidnapped and an old Sith book is discovered that may mean the end of the Republic.
description.15: The Secret Defenders get two new team members! Look out evil, here comes Giant-Man and Iron Fist!
description.16: The unthinkable has happened - Wonder Man has fallen! And his replacement raises more questions than answers! Who is the enigmatic Century?
description.21: Daredevil's final showdown with System Crash! And, alongside Captain America, DD discovers the villainous organization's true allegiance...amongst the ranks of Hydra!
description.22: The climatic conclusion to the Douglock Chronicles! With the destruction of Stryfe's old base imminent, how will Excalibur be able to save the humans and Zero?
description.23: There's no showdown in the universe that the Hulk can't smash his way out of. But there are some problems that even his great strength can't punch through, as Banner's old friend Jim Wilson experiences a shocking crisis.
description.24: Vor/Tex downloads his consciousness into Tony's body and traps him in cyberspace.
description.26: Punisher has to bail on capturing his enemies, and take the last flight off Puerto Dulce before it's too late.
description.30: The team finds themselves reliving one of their greatest battles...the first clash against Galactus! Can the FF even hope to prevail without the genius of Reed Richards to guide them?
description.38: As the Externals pressure Cannonball to join their team and to give them the cure to the Legacy Virus, Cable and Domino decide they need to find a new base for the X-Force team. Will Cannonball abandon his teammates?
description.40: Will Dr. Stevens merge with his true, better half... Doctor Strange?
description.42: Shriek brings out the worst in Malcolm McBride, forcing him to become his violent alter ego, Carrion! Meanwhile, Peter finds his life collapsing in the wake of Aunt May's health crisis. This is Spider-Man as you've never seen him before- violent, angry, and dead set on vengeance!
description.43: Quicksilver is confronted by a person from his past who has reformed their anti-mutant sentiments. Plus, the Circle of Paqvane decides to teach Quicksilver another difficult lesson!
description.44: Cable...son of the Goblin Queen? That's what the evil sorcerer Belasco says, and if it's true, only Cable can stop sinister forces from creating a portal that will link Earth with the demonic realm of Limbo!
description.45: Will the New Warriors, lost across time and space, finally find their way back home with the pack of new members?
description.49: When'Star Wars'hit the big screen in'1977, the world fell in love with'Artoo-Detoo'and'See-Threepio. Now the events that led them to their fateful meeting with'Luke Skywalker'are revealed for the first time! In this issue, Corellian'rogue'Jace Forno'leases the dysfunctional duo for a deadly mission to the'moon'Indobok!
description.55: Count Abyss betrays his former underling, Maya, and takes her captive! It's up to the Infinity Watch to save her, but first they'll have to cut through a seemingly endless horde of Count Abyss' demons!
description.57: Daredevil's war against System Crash continues! Every step takes him closer to the man pulling the strings- but little does Matt know that man is none other than Baron von Strucker, of the sinister organization Hydra! Guest-starring Captain America and the Ragin' Cajun, Gambit of the X-Men!
description.58: Surrounded by Stryfe's robots, Zero teleports Excalibur and everyone else to safety! Meanwhile, on Muir Island, Professor X and Moira make a startling discovery about the Legacy Virus!
description.59: The Hulk is ambushed by an unexpected foe - Talos, the mighty Skrull warrior! But what is Talos' reason for attacking the Hulk unprovoked - aside from the obvious death wish, of course!
description.60: Tony battles Vor/Tex in cyberspace. Featuring the X-Men.
description.62: Now out of prison, Punisher, Ice, and Microchip must escape a deadly island crawling with commandos…and quickly.
description.64: Don Blake is appalled by the years that have passed, and holds Thor personally responsible for shaving years off his life!
description.67: As if being stranded in the future wasn't trouble enough, Susan, Ben, and Johnny discover that they are in the future...of an alternate Earth! And to set things right, they will have to face off with a familiar, yet unstoppable foe - the Devourer of Worlds himself, GALACTUS!
description.68: Iceman's body may have woken up, but the person inside is...the White Queen?!
description.72: What happens when the robot you've created becomes self-aware and overrides all of your programming? Ask Dr. Hawkins-Mailer, who's Nimrod has gone out of control and is attacking our heroes!
description.75: The return of Clea! Strange’s former student and partner needs the help of Earth’s Sorcerer Supreme! But which one?
description.79: The West Coast Avengers are no more, but Iron Man has plans of his own for a new team, and a new philosophy! They will actively prevent disasters before they happen, rather than stopping them. They are…Force Works!
description.83: The Sunrise Society strikes! With Mace's life and Venom's Underground both on the line, the pair of anti-heroes decide to join forces!
description.84: Beware the shrill cry of Shriek! Spider-Man must rescue Malcolm McBride from the delusional villain holding him captive. How does John Jameson play a part in Spidey's plan? Plus, a heated confrontation between Aunt May and MJ!
description.85: A Crystal-centric issue! Crystal must save fellow inhuman Sporr from mad geneticist Terrigene. Who is Terrigene? And why is she so insistent on having Sporr's DNA for herself?
description.86: Stranded in the Florida swamps, Cable and Lee Forrester struggle to survive! And if that's not enough, finding shelter in a small cottage only leads them to more despair!
description.89: Blade, Ghost Rider, and Morbius team with Doctor Strange against Verdelet!
description.94: The “New” New Warriors—Darkhawk, Dagger, Bandit, Hindsight Lad, Turbo, and Powerpax—must rescue Justice, Speedball, and Nova!
description.95: In a deadly case of mistaken identity,'See-Threepio'and'Artoo-Detoo become entangled in an illegal operation on the'Hosk'moon, and are forced to enter a'droid'battle arena!
description.99: Adam Warlock…in love!? It seems Adam has fallen for the mysterious woman known as Maya, but little does he know that he is playing right into the hands of Count Abyss!

1.text: Nightwatch, teaming up with Venom? You better believe this cover, True Believers, because this is the real deal!

3.text: Wolverine and Boom Boom must protect a local nuclear power plant from a group of teens against technology. Can the two mutants mediate the situation before it turns dire?

5.text: As the Infinity Watch draws closer to the inevitable showdown with Count Abyss, truths of the villains past are brought to light. Witness the untold origins of the sinister Count Abyss!

6.text: FIGHTING CHANCE BOOK 6 Does Cap stand a chance against the combined forces of Damon Dran and Americop?

7.text: SINS OF THE PAST PART 1 When Black Tom's men break into Deadpool's favorite bar to kidnap the Merc, Siryn and Banshee show up to help Deadpool out. But with Deadpool's healing factor on the fritz, can he survive?

SINS OF THE PAST PART 1 When Black Tom's men break into Deadpool's favorite bar to kidnap the Merc, Siryn and Banshee show up to help Deadpool out. But with Deadpool's healing factor on the fritz, can he survive?

8.text: Phineas Thomas Horton is a brilliant inventor on the  brink of great discovery! Like a modern day Prometheus, Horton, unlocking the secrets of creation, hands the world a Human Torch! This is the beginning of Marvels!

9.text: Gabe O’ Hara knows his brother is Spider-Man, but can he keep the secret? While Gabe and Miguel recover from their adventure in Cyberspace, Kasey Nash is confronted by Stark- Fujikawa with a corporate deal she can’t refuse. Plus, Miguel’s first love, Xina Kwan is back on the scene! But what is the reason for her return?

10.text: Thor and Thunderstrike are aided by Don Blake in their battle against the Destroyer!

14.text: Thanos has assembled the mightiest cosmic warriors for this very moment- the destruction of Tyrant, the most powerful being in the galaxy! But will Terrax, Jack, Ganymede and Legacy object to being Thanos’ pawns? And when Thanos takes on Tyrant alone, will the Titan walk away victorious? Will he walk away at all? The explosive conclusion to Cosmic Powers!

15.text: The Secret Defenders get two new team members! Look out evil, here comes Giant-Man and Iron Fist!

16.text: The unthinkable has happened - Wonder Man has fallen! And his replacement raises more questions than answers! Who is the enigmatic Century?

17.text: The Galactic Guardians assemble, realizing Martinex's dream of a new wave of cosmic defense.

18.text: One is an alien symbiote, sworn enemy of Spider-Man. The other is a broken man, who made a deal with the devil for power to destroy Ghost Rider. But when they are attacked by the Stalkers, Venom and Vengeance are ready to show that these are two dark doppelgangers you should NEVER mess with!

19.text: Rancor makes short work of the Guardians...and seizes control of the team!

20.text: When the Guardians lose a member, they're forced to find a replacement. Along the way, one of their own undergoes a drastic change.

26.text: Punisher has to bail on capturing his enemies, and take the last flight off Puerto Dulce before it's too late.

29.text: Polaris must make a life-ending choice to free Havok of Malice’s possession.

32.text: Wolverine and his allies must defend themselves against a pack of wolf-like creatures with major bloodlust!

36.text: In Apocalypse’s citadel, the consciousness of En Sabah Nur is being prepared for its new host, Stryfe. Meanwhile, teenager Nathan Dayspring is dying from the techno-organic virus that has plagued him since birth. After struggling between life and death, Nathan finds a way to exist on the astral plane, and encounters his half-sister Rachel Summers.

37.text: The first appearance of Deathtoll! Who is the mysterious new villain wreaking havoc for War Machine? And will Worldwatch be able to calculate his next move?

38.text: As the Externals pressure Cannonball to join their team and to give them the cure to the Legacy Virus, Cable and Domino decide they need to find a new base for the X-Force team. Will Cannonball abandon his teammates?

40.text: Will Dr. Stevens merge with his true, better half... Doctor Strange?

46.text: Arno Stark – Iron Man of the year 2020! After his debut in the pages of Machine Man (1984), the visionary (and distant cousin of Tony Stark), returns in this one-shot adventure! Seeking to take down a technical rival who will stop at nothing to destroy him, Arno finds that the cost of doing business may result in loss of life! Plus, a romance with the rival’s daughter Melodi may hit the skids if Arno doesn’t develop new tech fast enough!

47.text: Kevin Trench is Nightwatch! See how this stalker of crime takes down Venom and the Silent Shadows of Morelle Pharmaceuticals!

50.text: Sabretooth’s presence at the Institute sets off a chain reaction which results in Jubilee’s kidnapping. Shadowcat dives into the Morlock Tunnels to save her fellow X-girl. Which Morlock has laid stake in Jubilee? And will Kitty Pryde be able to tackle this mission on her own?

52.text: FIGHTING CHANCE BOOK 5 Americop! Kono the Sumo! A few reasons why Cap has gone down the beaten path!

53.text: Introducing the Maryjanes, a trio of cyber-punk women so tough, they give Spider-Man a run for his money! Will Spider-Man 2099 be able to take down these cold-blooded killers...and save the public from their cyborg weaponry? Plus, Gabe O’ Hara discovers the true identity of Spider-Man!

54.text: Typhoid Mary, loose in Manhattan! Surviving an earlier encounter with the villainess, Spider-Man chases down Typhoid and finds her preparing the next slaughter! Spidey intervenes, but can the already-defeated web-slinger handle a second round with Mary, quite contrary?

55.text: Count Abyss betrays his former underling, Maya, and takes her captive! It's up to the Infinity Watch to save her, but first they'll have to cut through a seemingly endless horde of Count Abyss' demons!

62.text: Now out of prison, Punisher, Ice, and Microchip must escape a deadly island crawling with commandos…and quickly.

66.text: Havok, under the influence of Malice, fights the love of his life, Polaris!

69.text: Back in Canada, a wolf-like creature terrorizes Wolverine and his friends as Logan looks to put his affairs in order.

72.text: What happens when the robot you've created becomes self-aware and overrides all of your programming? Ask Dr. Hawkins-Mailer, who's Nimrod has gone out of control and is attacking our heroes!

77.text: A turning-point issue! In possession of the Moebius Stone, Malachi embraces his megalomaniacal nature to its fullest- and the world trembles. A new leader of the Secret Defenders appointed! But who?

78.text: Tyrant attempts mind control over Morg, a devoted herald of Galactus. Will Morg find himself with a new master…and the Power Cosmic? Ganymede agrees to help Thanos in his takedown of Tyrant. But Jack of Hearts and Legacy have tracked down Ganymede- straight into Tyrant’s fortress!

79.text: The West Coast Avengers are no more, but Iron Man has plans of his own for a new team, and a new philosophy! They will actively prevent disasters before they happen, rather than stopping them. They are…Force Works!

80.text: Blade thought he could start a new life in New York City, free of vampire hunting. But when he's confronted with a group of new and deadly vampire drug dealers, he'll learn just how much the world needs the Daywalker!

82.text: Will the Hawk God keep Aleta and Stakar alive and/or physically fused? How serious is Talon´s back injury? Will Mephisto and Malevolence procure his amulet? Vance´s new suit - Yondu´s ultimate allegiance - the Beyonder´s destiny! And ultimately, how will the final fate of the Protégé impact on all of this? You can be sure Eternity, Scathan the Celestial and the Living Tribunal will be heard from before all is said and done!

83.text: The Sunrise Society strikes! With Mace's life and Venom's Underground both on the line, the pair of anti-heroes decide to join forces!

88.text: Richard Rider fights himself from an alternate timeline! Which Nova will emerge victorious?

89.text: Blade, Ghost Rider, and Morbius team with Doctor Strange against Verdelet!

91.text: It is now eight years since Rachel Summers transported Scott “Slym”, and Jean “Redd”, into the future. Nathan Dayspring continues to hone his telepathic powers under the tutelage of his mother, but wonders why his parents insist he hide his cybernetic arm. After discovering that his parents are involved in a secret rebellion, Nathan must determine if he should side with his family, or Apocalypse.

92.text: Cetewayo meets a permanent end at the hands of the Advisor, prompting War Machine to carry the torch of his fallen ally. Plus, War Machine continues to expand Worldwatch, and invites Sheva Joseph to join his staff.

93.text: The epic crossover concludes with Spider-Man and X-Factor’s final battle to reveal the inner workings of Project: Homegrown.

96.text: Spider-Man 2099 vs. Cyberspace! After discovering that his brother is involuntarily hooked into a virtual reality, Miguel must retrieve Gabe from malicious software. Will Spider-Man 2099 be able to stay the course on his most personal mission yet?

97.text: While on assignment for the Daily Bugle, Spider-Man comes across a distressed young woman and invites her back to his home. Once invited inside by Mary Jane, the young woman is revealed to be none other than Typhoid Mary! Both Spidey and his love are in serious peril!

98.text: FIGHTING CHANCE BOOK 4 The Sentinel of Liberty-crushed by Americop!

99.text: Adam Warlock…in love!? It seems Adam has fallen for the mysterious woman known as Maya, but little does he know that he is playing right into the hands of Count Abyss!
